Plot: Rosemary and Guy Woodhouse, an ordinary young couple, settle into a New York City apartment, unaware that the elderly neighbors and their bizarre group of friends have taken a disturbing interest in them. But by the time Rosemary discovers the horrifying truth, it may be far too late!
Characters: Rosemary Woodhouse, Guy Woodhouse, Minnie Castevet, Roman Castevet
Setting: New York City, New York (United States), Upper West Side, Manhattan, New York (United States)
